<a href='http://www.ukclimbing.com/articles/page.php?id=9149' title='Read full article'><img src='https://cdn.ukclimbing.com/t/289357.jpg' width='150' height='105' alt='thumb' border='1' align='left' hspace='8' /></a>Arc'teryx is proud to announce the Lakeland Revival will be taking place for the fourth year running, beginning on the 29th April and ended on the 31st August. The aim of the revival is still simple, to revive the spirit of Lakeland climbing and encourage people to come and enjoy the climbing the Lakes has to offer.